content: Bad, not good. Literally "not the best".
A priviledged adjective. It can modify a noun in front rather than with a "more on the X side (of things)" construction.
O, riby a ŕyzhy. Ŕyzhy bęńy.
Cup-of-joe wise, would you give it a quick little whip up, real quick?
No (of course), no question, I'm on it.
